data.description: Come see the 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bathroom Transitional home located in the Ivy Farms subdivision of Newport News. Only minutes away from interstate access, shopping, Sandy Bottom Park and more!! This home spacious home is tucked in a cul-de-sac that has a large fenced in backyard with deck great for entertaining on those warm summer days and a wood burning stove to cozy up to on those cold winter nights. This home has a newer hot water heater and roof, Stainless Steel appliances, a large master bedroom with 2 closets and more. Come see everything this home has to offer today!
